<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefadab07-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s312101"><num value="312101">§ 312101.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this chapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idefadab08-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s312101/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">Board</inline>.—</heading><content>The term “Board” means the board of trustees of the National Trust.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idefadab09-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s312101/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">National trust</inline>.—</heading><content>The term “National Trust” means the National Trust for Historic Preservation in the United States established under <ref href="/us/usc/t54/s312102">section 312102 of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idefadab0a-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db">(<ref href="/us/pl/113/287/s3">Pub. L. 113–287, § 3</ref>, <date date="2014-12-19">Dec. 19, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/3249">128 Stat. 3249</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
